SIMPLE: existent
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Existent
<hw>Ex*ist"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>existens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>existere</ets>.
See <er>Exist</er>.]</ety> <def>Having being or existence; existing;
being; occurring now; taking place.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The eyes and mind are fastened on objects which have no real
being, as if they were truly <qex>existent</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Existential</ent>⟦br⟧
